{"lang":"cpp","typed_code":"class Solution {\nprotected:\n  bool palindromicCheck(string s) {\n    int n = s.size();\n    for (int i = 0; i < n / 2; i++) {\n      if (s[i] != s[n - i - 1]) {\n        return false;\n      }\n    }\n    return true;\n  }\n\npublic:\n  string longestPalindrome(string s) {\n    string ans = \"\";\n    for (int i = 0; i < s.size(); i++) {\n      for (int j = ans.size() + 1; j <= s.size() - i; j++) {\n        if (s[i] != s[i + j - 1]) {\n          continue;\n        }\n        string subStr = s.substr(i, j);\n        if (palindromicCheck(subStr)) {\n          ans = subStr;\n        }\n      }\n    }\n    return ans;\n  }\n};","question_id":"5","data_input":false}